", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States went into the competition seeking out simply one medal, but to dream of finishing with two runners on the podium, something the nation had not done since 1912, felt like a faraway fantasy.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9443044347577181, \"rank\": 0.047515274016892095, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"simply one medal\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"dream\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"two runners\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"a faraway fantasy\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream NBC 5 for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stream\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Hocker and Nuguse gave it everything they had right up until the final stages of the competition, and you can watch it all on primetime on NBC Chicago Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.6941588962486702, \"rank\": 0.4059388755408542, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.